# Follow redirects | Examples | REST client | kdb Insights Core - kdb products

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/insights/core/kurl/appendix/follow_redirects.html

# Follow redirects

Make a call to get the code.kx.com main webpage without following redirects.
This will return a 301 Moved Permanently: the new location is
`https://code.kx.com/q/`.

    
    
    resp:.kurl.sync ("https://code.kx.com/"; `GET; ``response_headers!(::;1b))
    show resp 0
    show "\r\n" vs resp 2
    

With redirection following enabled, this returns the main page.

    
    
    resp2:.kurl.sync ("https://code.kx.com/"; `GET; ``follow_redirects!(::;1b))
    show resp2
    

